Hello this a github repo , with basic functions and opearions to help you get started with Nodejs , Express and MongoDb.

The dependancies included are :
Nodemon : for auto tracking changes made , without having to cut down and restart the server.
express :built upon Nodejs , a very popular package for server side functions.
Body-parser : For parsing the request body , beacuse express doesn't parse the json , by default.
express-validator : for server side validations.
mongoose : for connecting to mongoDb.
dotenv : for storing env variables in a sepearte file with ext .env.
morgan : a middleware , which makes it easier to view the request logs.

